description: Seattle Cookie Counter caters delicious ice cream sandwiches that everyone can and will enjoy! All of our treats just happens to be vegan and we offer plenty of delicious gluten free and soy free options as well. We use at least 95% organic ingredients and local whenever possible. We offer unique & traditional flavors like Snickerdoodle Vanilla, Gluten Free PB&J;, and Sugar Cookie Lavender. Our '74 VW Bus with its built in counter top, hand crocheted heart garland, vintage ice cream sign, and music bring all the charm!
name: Seattle Cookie Counter
